Of course, ID has to move from its position of ignorance, to a position which allows it to be fully reconcilable with science, namely by arguing a position of 'front loading' which moves the design event to coincide with the Big Bang.Neat to see how ID proponents have come to move towards a more scientific position, although it does render the ID position to a status of fully religious.